<li id="cite_note-43"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-43">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFCuadrilla_Resources_Ltd" class="citation web cs1">Cuadrilla Resources Ltd. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20161028025458/http://www.cuadrillaresources.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Chemical-Disclosure-PH-1.jpg">"Composition of Bowland Shale Hydraulic Fracturing Fluid for Preese Hall-1 well"</a>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cuadrillaresources.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/Chemical-Disclosure-PH-1.jpg">the original</a> on 28 October 2016<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">4 April</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Composition+of+Bowland+Shale+Hydraulic+Fracturing+Fluid+for+Preese+Hall-1+well&amp;rft.au=Cuadrilla+Resources+Ltd&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuadrillaresources.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F02%2FChemical-Disclosure-PH-1.jpg&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFracking+in+the+United+Kingdom" class="Z3988"></span></span>
