<li id="cite_note-120"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-120">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFChief_Inspector_of_Drinking_Water2013" class="citation report cs1">Chief Inspector of Drinking Water (July 2013). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dwi.defra.gov.uk/about/annual-report/2012/private-england.pdf">Drinking water 2012: Private water supplies in England</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> (Report). Drinking Water Inspectorate<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">16 October</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=report&amp;rft.btitle=Drinking+water+2012%3A+Private+water+supplies+in+England&amp;rft.pub=Drinking+Water+Inspectorate&amp;rft.date=2013-07&amp;rft.au=Chief+Inspector+of+Drinking+Water&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdwi.defra.gov.uk%2Fabout%2Fannual-report%2F2012%2Fprivate-england.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFracking+in+the+United+Kingdom" class="Z3988"></span></span>
